#: ./doc/src/docbkx/common/glossary.xml842(glossterm)
msgid "subdomain"
msgstr ""

#: ./doc/src/docbkx/common/glossary.xml844(para)
msgid ""
"A domain within a parent domain. Subdomains cannot be registered. Subdomains"
" allow you to delegate domains. Subdomains can themselves have subdomains, "
"so third-level, fourth-level, fifth-level, and deeper levels of nesting are "
"possible."
